Nia, tell us the heritage of your name.

00:17:37.056 --> 00:17:40.359 line:95%,end
May I please ask you what that word means?

00:17:42.428 --> 00:17:44.396 line:95%,end
ABBY: <i>I don't think any</i>
<i>of my students are great</i>

00:17:44.463 --> 00:17:46.165 line:95%,end
<i>at the whole pageant thing.</i>

00:17:46.231 --> 00:17:49.301 line:5%,start
We spent so much time on technique,

00:17:49.368 --> 00:17:51.837 line:95%,end
that I never really get a lot of time

00:17:51.904 --> 00:17:53.906 line:95%,end
to do the interview skills.

00:17:53.972 --> 00:17:57.776 line:95%,end
