The most important thing
is that you do not panic.

00:18:05.717 --> 00:18:08.687 line:95%,end
Pull your thoughts together,
take a deep breath,

00:18:08.754 --> 00:18:10.122 line:95%,end
and answer the question.

00:18:10.189 --> 00:18:11.890 line:95%,end
Does everyone understand?

00:18:12.491 --> 00:18:14.226 line:95%,end
-(blows whistle)
