-CATHY: Yeah. So, when was chalkboard?
-...that you missed your flight?

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:22.995 line:95%,end
-CATHY: Two days ago?
-Two days ago.

00:19:23.061 --> 00:19:24.429 line:95%,end
So where have you been the last two days?

00:19:24.496 --> 00:19:26.165 line:95%,end
I don't think it's a big deal.
I missed my flight.

