00:19:40.846 --> 00:19:42.381 line:95%,end
But you're not in the duet. Right?

00:19:42.447 --> 00:19:43.515 line:95%,end
You're not in the duet.

00:19:43.582 --> 00:19:45.284 line:95%,end
Here we go again as a group.

00:19:45.350 --> 00:19:47.452 line:95%,end
