00:19:49.555 --> 00:19:51.823 line:95%,end
have to discuss it with Abby,
then we will.

00:19:51.890 --> 00:19:53.025 line:95%,end
-But you know what?
-CATHY: I understand this whole--

00:19:53.091 --> 00:19:54.493 line:95%,end
We're in this room and it's a team.

00:19:54.560 --> 00:19:56.061 line:95%,end
