00:20:03.202 --> 00:20:06.605 line:95%,end
Because I get so sick and tired
of hearing you guys--

00:20:06.672 --> 00:20:08.173 line:95%,end
it's a team. It's a group.
It's a team. It's a group.

00:20:08.240 --> 00:20:11.877 line:95%,end
Yet, Vivi is not really
in any of your numbers.

00:20:11.944 --> 00:20:14.413 line:95%,end
