-I have a comment.

00:20:35.834 --> 00:20:36.935 line:95%,end
Then if you don't care
what I have to say--

00:20:37.002 --> 00:20:38.036 line:95%,end
HOLLY: I don't care what you have to say.

00:20:38.103 --> 00:20:39.104 line:95%,end
Then you need to be quiet.

00:20:39.171 --> 00:20:41.873 line:95%,end
