your hand up her butt

00:20:43.842 --> 00:20:45.677 line:95%,end
and beat her ventriloquist.

00:20:45.744 --> 00:20:46.945 line:95%,end
Well, then do something about it.

00:20:49.715 --> 00:20:50.549 line:95%,end
HOLLY: <i>I'm frustrated for Melissa,</i>

00:20:50.616 --> 00:20:52.884 line:95%,end
<i>because she is not</i>
<i>sticking up for herself.</i>

00:20:52.951 --> 00:20:54.419 line:5%,start
I don't believe in being a doormat.

00:20:54.486 --> 00:20:56.788 line:5%,start
It's frustrating to see
other people be doormats.

00:20:56.855 --> 00:20:58.323 line:95%,end
But if Melissa wants to be a doormat

00:20:58.390 --> 00:21:00.659 line:95%,end
and have people walk
all over her, so be it.

00:21:00.726 --> 00:21:01.760 line:95%,end
I am done.

00:21:01.827 --> 00:21:06.531 line:95%,end
Even though Abby pulled a duet
and the duet didn't dance,

00:21:06.598 --> 00:21:10.102 line:95%,end
I'm here right now to support your teams.

00:21:10.168 --> 00:21:11.737 line:95%,end
That's all that matters.

00:21:11.803 --> 00:21:12.971 line:95%,end
Come on, Vivi, let's go.

00:21:13.038 --> 00:21:14.206 line:95%,end
Thank you very much, Cathy.

00:21:14.273 --> 00:21:16.041 line:95%,end
-MELISSA: Right?
-CATHY: I'm here for the awards.

00:21:16.108 --> 00:21:17.342 line:95%,end
-HOLLY: Thank you.
-KELLY: Oh, yay.

00:21:17.409 --> 00:21:19.511 line:95%,end
