00:21:37.396 --> 00:21:40.899 line:5%,start
My mom, the one and only
Maryen Lorrain, is home.

00:21:40.966 --> 00:21:42.534 line:5%,start
-DANCE MOM: (laughs) Hi.
-Hey.

00:21:42.601 --> 00:21:46.138 line:95%,end
ABBY: My mom is a gracious lady

00:21:46.772 --> 00:21:49.841 line:95%,end
