00:21:49.908 --> 00:21:51.877 line:95%,end
Grab a plate on that end.

00:21:51.943 --> 00:21:53.745 line:95%,end
Go through the line. Take your food.

00:21:53.812 --> 00:21:56.548 line:95%,end
(upbeat music playing)

00:21:57.282 --> 00:21:59.685 line:95%,end
ABBY: I understand that Cathy's busy,

