I love the big watermelon game.

00:22:22.441 --> 00:22:23.709 line:95%,end
KELLY: You got the biggest
watermelon you could find.

00:22:23.775 --> 00:22:24.609 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: Oh, my!

00:22:24.676 --> 00:22:25.844 line:95%,end
Okay. Just go.

00:22:25.911 --> 00:22:27.813 line:95%,end
<i>You put grease all over the watermelon</i>

00:22:27.879 --> 00:22:29.514 line:95%,end
<i>and you throw them in the pool.</i>

00:22:30.349 --> 00:22:31.817 line:95%,end
(screams)

00:22:31.883 --> 00:22:34.486 line:95%,end
ABBY: <i>The goal of the game</i>
<i>is to grab the watermelon</i>

00:22:34.553 --> 00:22:36.922 line:95%,end
and get out of the pool
with the watermelon in your hands.

00:22:36.988 --> 00:22:39.358 line:95%,end
